## 📌 Overview
Perfect E-commerce Store is a custom-built WordPress theme designed for modern online stores.  
It is fully responsive, performance-optimized, and compatible with WooCommerce.

This theme is ideal for:
- Online stores
- Small to medium eCommerce businesses
- Product showcase websites

---

## ✨ Features
- Custom WordPress theme development (no page builder dependency)
- Fully responsive design (Mobile, Tablet, Desktop)
- WooCommerce integration
- Clean and optimized code
- Fast loading performance
- SEO-friendly structure
- Cross-browser compatibility
- Custom templates and reusable components

