## ⚙️ Installation
1. Download or clone the perfect-ecommerce-store-pro
2. Copy theme folder into:
   `/wp-content/themes/`
3. Go to WordPress Admin → Appearance → Themes
4. Activate the theme
5. Install and activate WooCommerce plugin

